TableGodBoardText.Text: A Seaside Walk With Yuelia
That bird's huge! I'm so happy!
Looks like someone's picked some feathers at the coast. A big bird's feathers...? Interesting!
A Blue Wind at Night
What a lovely breeze! I'm going for the next one.
A blue wind howling in the night... The new wind calls to me.
Huntin' Pete's Heroic Adventure
You actually won... You really are something...! I want to be just like you...
Shouldn't have bragged... Whether you can defeat that bird remains to be seen... Wouldn't want me to come too, would you...?
I Want to Craft a Beautiful Dress â
You got me some! I'm so happy!
I want to craft a formal dress. Is there anyone that could get me some vivid blue material?
A Hunter's Crusade Request â
Thought it would be pretty tough, but of course you handled it.
This is a really dangerous quest. Everyone who takes it on becomes frozen. You have to be very careful.
A Nighttime Investigation With Lusica
So "the moving moon" was actually a Lunaria! It's been a great night!
There's been rumors lately that the moon starts moving around when night falls. This needs to be investigated!
Blue Shoes
Thank you very much! Please take this.
That vivid shade of blue is hard to forget... All I want is, while I still have the inspiration, to find someone to get it for me.
I Want to Craft a Beautiful Dress â¡
You got me some! Thank you!
That formal dress the Tailor crafted was super popular with everyone! It would be great if you could help me with it again in the future.
A Hunter's Crusade Request â¡
Absolutely stunning. I knew you could do it.
Yet another dangerous quest! It's going to try to put you to sleep. Get ready.
The Spirit of Water's Call
Oh, you're good.
Wanna challenge the Spirit of Water? You'll find it near that rocky reef. Proceed carefully.
A Giant Blue Tree Glittering on the Shore
I knew you'd succeed.
How about a new trial for you. The blue great tree you find on the coast... can you cut it down?
Horns Flash Off the Sea
Woohoo! That was beautiful!
Got a special trial for you. Time to see the results of your daily training!
A Water Wingstone Surging With the Ocean
Good job! I've never mined it before. Gwahahaha!
For enhancing Water-type gear, this is just the thing. Go on!
Gourmeow Gossip
Thanks a Meowllion! Food purrty tonight!
The cats say a new fish has appeared! Hope somebody brings me some right meow!
Purchase Request: Wood
Thank you! You really helped me out! Here's a gift for you.
I'm out of wood. I'd like to ask someone to bring me some.
Purchase Request: Ore
Thank you. This really helps. Please accept this.
I need help making a purchase. Can anyone help me?
Purchase Request: Thread Â· Cloth
Thank you very much! This should be right! Here's a thank you from me!
I'm all out of thread and cloth... What do I do now...?
Intervening in a Turf Dispute â
You made it? Huh?! Isn't that something!
We've been having all these swaggering pirates hanging around. It's been quite unpleasant...
Intervening in a Turf Dispute â¡
You prevented the city getting destroyed! Thank you so much!
Well they're furious about the islands, so they're going around committing savage attacks. We can't let them destroy this city.
Intervening in a Turf Dispute â¢
Is it finally over?! Tomorrow will be business as usual then!
See all the fish around here, next time they're all mine to try... Ugh! My Campfire Fish!
Objective: to Be a Stronger Self â
You got everything ready! Thanks!
Seeing your growth pushes me to want to work harder too. So, I'll start over with learning about gear...
Objective: to Be a Stronger Self â¡
Thank you so, so much! Hopefully this will make even me stronger...
Soon I'll put on armor and leg guards then... They will make me stronger... probably...
Fresh Seafood â
Oh yeah! Let's see... It goes very well with barley juice! Thank you for your hospitality.
Hear there's a fresh batch of fish at the port. I'd like a bit of everything. Could you get me some?
Fresh Seafood â¡
Lemme have some of this... So tender! I can't get enough! Thank you for your hospitality.
I'm really hankering for a good seafood dish.
Fresh Seafood â¢
Mmm it's all so fresh! I could eat this all day! Okay, okay enough!
I wanna eat till I can't move. Do me a favor... Get me a seafood platter so I can try a bit of everything.
A Banquet for Pirates
This is right here! A gorgeous feast and barley juice! You've really done us a solid!
The banquet needs barley juice and a feast! I need them to get ahead! I can depend on your help with that right?
Picking Flowers From the Coast
You really brought them! Thank you very much!
Got a birthday in my family. I wanted to organize a nice floral arrangement as a gift. but I'm tied up with work...
Something Special for My Daughter
This will make everyone happy at home... You really helped me out. Please accept this.
Thinking about getting a gift for my daughter... It should be something cute. Please bring me something girls like.
The Glistening Item
Thank you! Here, it's a gift for you!
I want some glittering coral! Can anyone help?!
Kiraby CoastâFireworks Show
Thanks! Greatâª I'll take care of the bigger fireworks. Come on, let's put on a show!
This is terrible...! I don't have enough fireworks for the show. Can you please find some?
Flamel's Bombastic Show â
Aha! What's a good time without a bang or ten?!
Boom! Alchemy is an explosion! So I'm hoping you'll come back with some bombs!
Flamel's Bombastic Show â¡
That's it alright! The bigger the bang the better!
Boom! Alchemy is a bombastic explosion! So I'm hoping you'll come back with the bombs I want!
Help With Renovations â
Yes, that's it! That's exactly the kind of tables and chairs I'm going for! Thanks a million!
I just moved to this seaport town but the furniture and room styles clash. I want new furniture for housewarming.
Help With Renovations â¡
No way, you actually found them! Wow, thank you so much! I'll have sweet dreams tonight.
I've been having trouble sleeping lately... and since the room is completely redone, I've just decided I'll get a new bed too.
Help With Renovations â¢
Thank you! It's great that I know I can ask you to help me move this heavy furniture.
I'm so nearly at the room of my dreams! I'm sorry, would you do me one more favor?
The Woodcutter's Worry â
So, that's it then, huh? My daughter's at a tricky age. Time to dress up a bit and see what she's up to.
My daughter has recently asked me if I could dress a little better... Can anyone tell me what outfits look good?!
The Woodcutter's Worry â¡
Okay, okay...! It'd be great if my daughter likes this...!
It's decided. I'll do a full outfit and see what she thinks. Can you help me out?!
Intervening in a Turf Dispute â£
Hahah! You really won! You're incredible! Amazing!
Those guys seem ready to figure out an end to this dispute... I'll pray for you.
To Become a Fine Woodcutter â
You passed the first trial! I knew you could do it.
Now that you've gained some experience as a Woodcutter, I'll give you 5 trials to try your hand at. I'll also give you some special gear once you complete them.
To Become a Fine Woodcutter â¡
Good. You passed the second trial as well. I knew you could do it.
The second trial is about Westwood. Have a heart-to-heart with a Palm Tree and bring me proof of it.
To Become a Fine Woodcutter â¢
Wow! You passed the third trial too! I knew you could do it.
For the third Trial, head to the Sacred Earth Tree for another heart-to-heart, then bring me proof of it.
To Become a Fine Woodcutter â£
Nice! You passed the fourth Trial too. I knew you could do it.
For the fourth trial, have a heart-to-heart with three trees, and once again bring me proof.
To Become a Fine Woodcutter â¤
You've now passed all trials and proved that you're an outstanding Woodcutter. Go on, this gear is all yours.
For your final trial, have a heart-to-heart with the Sacred Water Tree. Bring me proof of it after.
Stay true â
Lemme see here. No way, you passed!
Have you been fishing lately? How about a couple of trials to perk you up a bit? Don't go changin' now!
Stay true â¡
Lemme see here. No way, you passed!
It's not over yet. Next is this trial!
Stay true â¢
Lemme see here. No way, you passed!
Bet you're pretty tired huh? But a trial doesn't stop for anyone!
Stay true â£
Lemme see here. No way, you passed! Well done!
So: your final trial. Catch this one and you can consider yourself a famous fisher!
Calling for Fresh Fins!
Not bad, they're really fresh! I'll make a killing with these! Thanks, here's a gift.
I'm seeking Swordfish Fins, for special reasons. Oh yes, the fresher the better. Thanks in advance.
Feeling the Boon of Earth
I made something great out of the material you gave me! Thank you so much, I had a lovely time weaving! This is your gift.
I really want to do some weaving right now. I'd like to get my hands on some wood that senses the boon of earth... to use as reference.
The Fish Market's Attractive Wares
Amazing! So feisty too! Thank you!
I want to sell some fresh fish at the market. Please help me find some good, lively fish!
The Start of Halloween
Thanks. I'd like to share my secret recipe with you as a thank-you gift.
I want fresh pumpkin. Unfortunately though, it's out of season now.
The Work of the Palace Head Chef
Awesome~âª Just in time too, I'm hungryâª Oh, a recipe? Here you go~
I've been ordered to give out recipes for free. But why don't I take the chance to get some gifts tooâª
Is There An "And"?
Thank you very much. Here's a recipe to say thanks!
This note says pumpkin pudding... or is it pumpkin AND pudding? Either way, it's time to put out a call.
The Best Pumpkin Field
Wow this helps me a lot! I'm gifting you this entire pumpkin field. It has great scenery, but only that.
I want to till the best pumpkin field. It looks good now, but the pumpkins taste soo... Oh... I'm so hungry...
Debut of the Halloween Maskman!
Got the candy. I'm gifting you this mask recipe as thanks. This makes you a Halloween Maskman too.
I'm Ja- no, I'm the Halloween Maskman. Trick or treat!
Later, Halloween Maskman!
Awesome! Then, here's a new mask recipe for you. This one is for an enthusiastic red mask...
Wrong guy. I'm the Halloween Maskman. Hand over some candy if you want to open a new Halloween Door.
Short of Jokes! Halloween Maskman!
Thank you. This recipe is to say thanks. You know... a soldier does a little bit of everything. So, please enjoy Halloween.
Huh...? It's me. I'm not ordered to wear a costume, so I'll give you a request in my normal wear. Hope I can get some of that candy you got there.
One Mysterious Morning
Thank you, here's a gift. It was already right in front of the door by the time I noticed it. It was really strange.
Trick or treat! ...I really want to try saying that once. I'm looking for candy and snacks for this evening!
Craft a Halloween Outfit â
Kind of exciting, right~? I've made it into a recipe. It's a thank-you gift for youâª
I want to make a new Halloween-themed outfit~ Anything I could use as a reference~?
Craft a Halloween Outfit â¡
I really feel a bit restless... Well~ That's probably it.
I seriously have zero inspiration~! Please get me something Halloween-y~
Craft a Halloween Outfit â¢
Oh, maybe it feels kind of all over the place? Do you think the general idea's there?
I still need to gather more Halloween-themed items. Come lend a hand, anyone~
Craft a Halloween Outfit â£
Of course I've had my mind on that outfit design~! Look, this is a recipeâª
I'm now over Halloween. I prefer crackers... Gimme some crackers~
Craft a Halloween Outfit â¤
Got it!âª Soft and gooey and melt-in-your-mouthâª I need to think about this... The recipe ready~âª
I'm nearly there with getting the Halloween style just right. I'd like a treat too!
The Best Halloween Cooking?
Congratulations on obtaining such a fine house! You'll get to spend all day living like a pumpkin seed!
Seeking the most exquisite Halloween food. The most focused contestant to pass the screening will walk away with a beautiful new house!
Here Comes The Great Blackbird â
The cake and Kusa Mochi go very well together! Very good. I'll leave you with this! See you...!
Alright, Halloween Envoy... The Great Blackbird honors you with a visit! Come on, hand over the goodies!
Here Comes The Great Blackbird â¡
Thought cake and apple pie together would be too sweet... but paired pretty well. Have this for your reward...!
The Great Blackbird is back! Come on, hand over the goodies! Or else I might get up to some mischief!
Here Comes The Great Blackbird â¢
Cake and Bandit Steak... What a mingling of salt and sweet! I can't eat enough. Too dangerous... The Great Blackbird's out!
The Great Blackbird is back for thirds! Come on, hand over the goodies! Hand them over! Or else, I'll throw a tantrum!
Here Comes The Great Blackbird â£
Cake and a Giant Fried Egg huh... That's actually a good combination?! Here. Reward. Bye!
Everyone's favorite Great Blackbird is back again! Come on, hand over the goodies! Or else... I'll sit down here and cry!
Here Comes The Great Blackbird â¤
You're really enjoying Halloween huh! You're only second-happiest in Reveria though. Who's number one? Shh, that's a secretâª
You've been kept waiting, but finally: The Great Blackbird! Come on, hand over the goodies! This is the final challenge!
Plan a Beautiful Bash for Her!
Yeah, perfect. It's very elegant, don't you think? Hopefully she'll be happy too.
I want to have a Halloween bash with her. Would anyone help us out with cooking?
Plan a Beautiful Bash for Him!
I gathered all this favorites! Nothing for Halloween though... Wonder if he'll be happy with everything?
I want to have a Halloween bash with him. Would anyone help us out with cooking?
Help a Furniture Merchant in Crisis â
I'm so grateful! Here's your gift. ...but that's hardly the tip of the iceberg. Please bring me some more~!
We have a Halloween event, but not enough candy to hand out! Please help~!
Help a Furniture Merchant in Crisis â¡
You saved us! This gift is for you. We keep welcoming in more and more kids though. Please help me get more candy~!
The kids were screaming for treats so I impulsively promised them prizes. Please help~!
Help a Furniture Merchant in Crisis â¢
Also, here. A gift for you! The shop is turning into a madhouse... Guess the commotion is not over yet~!
Adults want in on the action too. It's a mess out there~! No way there's enough treats and prizes for everyone~!
Help a Furniture Merchant in Crisis â£
Here, a gift for you! We're closing for the day once all the things have been handed out~! But we must have secured great publicity.
All those treats and prizes turned this shop upside down~ Would you share some treats and prizes with me~?
Trick or Treat!
Yeaaah! Halloween is seriously awesome!
Trick or treat! Gimme a nice treat or I'll give you a nasty trick!
Trick or treat...?
Thank you, now I have treats for the kids. How can I thank you...?
Trick or treat. You'll make Fogey very annoyed, if you don't have any treats to spare.
An Annoying Halloween
My sister insisted I take it, then shoved it at me... Am I a child?!
Trick or treat... Uh, I'd be really glad if you gave me a treat.  But if you can't, that's fine.
Papa Bear's Halloween
Indeed, yes. Take it then! This one is a favorite. Yes, and I'll give this one to Mayna.
Ahaha! Happy Halloween! A special day, isn't it? I'll take your treats and give you something good in exchange!
Fabbie's Bright Idea â
Got the treats. Here you go, recipe. Let's trade more.
Happy Halloween? Fabbie has a great idea. Trade your treats for Fabbie's recipe?
Fabbie's Bright Idea â¡
Appreciate your treats. Take Fabbie's recipe. It's a gift. Happy Halloween.
Happy Halloween? Trade your treats for Fabbie's recipe? Fabbie's ready to trade.
Fabbie's Bright Idea â¢
Time for some trading. Take this recipe. Fabbie still has more to trade.
Happy Halloween? Come. Let's trade treats and recipes.
Fabbie's Bright Idea â£
Let's trade. Here's a recipe. Good. Fabbie is satisfied.
Happy Halloween? Trade Fabbie's recipe for a treat. This is the final one.
A Special Hictick Scheme â
Thanks for participating. Here, recipe for you. Please keep trading in future.
Hictick's special scheme for Halloween! Trade in recipes for treats and outfits. Looking forward to your participation!
A Special Hictick Scheme â¡
You're back for more! Then, take this recipe. It's a gift. Please try to gather them all!
Hictick's special scheme for Halloween! Trade in recipes for treats and outfits. There are still loads to exchange!
A Special Hictick Scheme â¢
Here. This is the last recipe. You got them all. Make sure to use them when making pairings.
Hictick's special scheme for Halloween! Trade in recipes for treats and outfits. This is the last batch!
Dragon Boy's Halloween
Thank you. Oh right, I should give you something in return. It's kind of big, but please take it.
Trick or treat! ...that's how you say it, right? Please give me treats then.
For All the Fans
Wow! Thank you! Um... Here are some special props! For completing the request!
I'm the powdery snow that falls on your heart: Snow! Do you accept my request?
Party Preparation â
Teeheeheeh, thank you! It didn't cost much, but here's my gift to you. I've got a same one for myselfâª
Don't you think Xmas party preparation is really interesting work? Do you want to help me out with the preparations?
Party Preparation â¡
We'll get to decorate the Xmas tree beautifully now! Oh, this recipe is for you! Try it out if you likeâª
I want lots of snow crystals on the Xmas tree. Does anyone have any Snow Shards?
Vida's Specs â
You went to so much trouble...! Thank you so much! Take these and put them on if you want.
My specs are broken... and need Snow Shards to repair.
Vida's Specs â¡
Thank you...! That should fix them up! Oh, you can take another pair if you want!
I'll need five more Snow Shards to repair these specs. Does anyone have any Snow Shards?
Gift Confusion â
Thanks! She should like it, right...? As long as the decor is cute?! Please accept my gift. It's a fireplace.
I got a present for my girlfriend, not sure if she'll like it though... Anyway I thought I'd at least wrap it in something cute.
Gift Confusion â¡
The "gift" is actually m-me. I was going to propose to her, but would it be risque to tie a ribbon around yourself...?
I couldn't get my girlfriend's gift wrapped up nicely enough. Can I make one more request, please!
Surprise Party â
Thank you. Here's a gift for you. Also, this surprise is for Lady Laura, so please keep it a secret.
King Erik and I are actually planning a party right now. Would you like to help out?
Surprise party â¡
Thank you. It won't be easy decorating the whole Palace. There's a lot to do.
We're still working on the party. We really don't have enough help. Anyone who wants to help is welcome.
Surprise Party â¢
Lady Laura will definitely be really happy to celebrate Xmas with the kids.
We'll invite a few of the town kids to the party and I'd appreciate if you could get some more socks as presents for them. And bells too!
Surprise Party â£
I really appreciate your willingness to help each time. All the preparation work should be done on time, thanks to you. It's not worth much, but I got you something to say thanks.
We're finally wrapping up the Castele Palace decoration mission. Please get the rest of the material ready.
Surprise Party â¤
We managed to get everything ready before Lady Laura arrives! Please accept this cape as my gift to you!
The party's about to start, but we have a problem. We didn't organize enough items! I'm sorry, but please quickly get more...!
Pippin's Gift
I'm so happy! Here you go, it's a gift! It's a collector's item!
Merry Xmas! I wish someone would exchange gifts with me!
Cawes' Gift
Thank you! I've always wanted this! Here you go. You have to treasure it.
Would anyone like to exchange gifts with me? My gift surely will not be disappointing.
Peco's Gift
Thank you so much! Here, take this. Peco also has a gift for you.
Merry Xmas! I'm looking for someone to exchange gifts with on this rare occasion.
Ralph's Gift
Woohoo! Ralph's so happy! Just look at this bow in Ralph's hand! Do you wanna try it out?
Merry Xmas. Here you go. This is good stuff. Ralph wants something too though.
Fabbie's Gift
Yeah~! Fabbie's soo happy! Here's something for all your efforts.
Would anyone like to exchange gifts with Fabbie? Fabbie wants to experience it too.
Hawley's Gift
Thank you. For you then, this fine collector's pickaxe.
Merry Xmas. I'd like to receive a gift from somebody too.
Kolding's Gift
Thank you. This beautiful axe is for you then.
Merry Xmas. Join me! We'll exchange gifts and have a good time.
Mead's Gift
Wow, awesome! Here's my gift for you! It's super great!
Merry Xmas. I want to find someone to exchange gifts with too. That's okay, right?
XmasâLive Concert
You really helped me out, thanks!âª Now I can put on a fabulous live concert for my fans!
The live concert venue is way too big. There's no way we have enough decor items. Is there anyone who would like to help?
Make It Sparkle â
Thank youâª We're about to make the classroom sparkle with Snow Shard decorâª Oh right, this gift is for you!
I want to celebrate Xmas with the other AoM students. We'll need Snow Shards. Does anyone have any?!
Make it Sparkle â¡
Heeheeâª Thanks! Yeah! Here you go: it's my favorite recipe!
We still need Snow Shards! Whoever can get us Snow Shards gets a collector's item gift!âª
Make It Sparkle â¢
You gathered a nice batch here!âª Aww, your hands look so cold... Alright, this recipe is for you!
I still don't have enough Snow Shards! This classroom has to be absolutely sparkling! Somebody help!
Make It Sparkle â£
Teeheehee, thanks!âª We're going to have a wonderful Xmas, thanks to you! Merry Xmas!
Okay, that's the last one! We need 15 more Snow Shards! The more the merrier!
Maid-factured â
You've been very helpful, thank you! I've been received really kindly here, so I'm planning to throw a party!
This year's party will be mind-blowing! My master is going to get a big surprise! Can you help out with the prep?
Maid-factured â¡
Perfect! My master's party is a go!
The party preparations are in the final stretch! I need to get my hands on additional decor items!
Heyho's Xmas Tree
Don't know if you can really consider it a present, but please have this tree. I had a great tree harvest this year.
Can you help me gather some decor for my Xmas tree? I can't do it all by myself.
A White Xmas â
Thank you, much better now. It's nice and warm inside this hood. Go on, try it on too.
This hood is way too warm. I'm burning up in here. I want something cold.
A White Xmas â¡
I can't stop looking at it! It's so pretty! We don't have anything like this where I'm from.
This is my first time seeing snow. It's so cold and and bright! I want even more.
A White Xmas â¢
Hey? You're telling me an old man named Santa Claus is the one going around gifting presents to people? I'm curious.
Heard it's Xmas now and you can receive presents. So I want Snow Shards.
A White Xmas â£
So I can't actually see him? No matter how many Snow Shards I get? Well, I'm going to find Santa Claus one day!
I'm looking for a man called Santa Claus, and I hear he can be found in a snow-covered place.
Charming Gift â
I don't even know why, but it's been ages and I still just can't resist this floaty Festive Ribbon.
It's that time of year again. Already! So, can you do me a favor?
Charming Gift â¡
Meow! I can't explain how good this feels! Take this gift.
Meow! Does anyone at all have some Festive Ribbon? If you do, please bring it to me ASAP.
Charming Gift â¢
Miaohahaha! You got it. You're a mind-reader now? You've come a long way! Jokes. Here, take this.
Alright then. You probably already know what I want right? I'm counting on you.
Charming Gift â£
Don't know how long it's been since I last exchanged gifts with anyone. Here, take it.
I got a pretty rare item here and I want to give it to someone. It's a special season; why don't we exchange gifts?
Kanna's Xmas â
Woohoo! Got the material! Thanks so much! This gift is for you! Please accept!
Got so much to do now! I haven't had time to gather any material though! Would anyone share some with me?
Kanna's Xmas â¡
Thanks! Something tells me I'll manage to put out a nice piece of furniture soon enough. Oh, and this is for you!
Can you help me gather more material? I'm sorry! I can't get away right now.
Kanna's Xmas â¢
A snowy winter is really beautiful. So I've made snow flooring that brings the experience indoors! Let me know what you think!
Alrighty! I know what to do! It's the best thing for winter! I'm going to need your help gathering the material!
Kanna's Xmas â£
Thanks! I'll try to make a gift Master Kennedy will be happy with!
I want to make a gift for Master Kennedy, but I don't have enough material. Would you please help me gather some! Please!
Kanna's Xmas â¤
Yes, yes! That's it! I'm super stoked to receive this material! Here, have a gift from me!
Wow, it's actually Xmas. Shall we exchange gifts? Guess you already know what I want, right?
The Bumbling Butler â
Very good...! Now there's no chance Master will reprimand me... Here, a small token of appreciation!
Master told me to organize some things, but I forgot! Please help me, kind Santa Claus!
The Bumbling Butler â¡
I appreciate you helping me over and over again...! Please allow me call you Santa Claus...!
Remember everything you got me the other day...? I misplaced them and can't find them now... Please, please help me!
Shards of Memories
Oh, here we are! I'm actually getting ready to propose to my girlfriend! Bells and Snow Shards are mementoes for us!
Hey! You over there! Wait up! I urgently need Snow Shards and Holy Bells! Give me some if you have! I'll thank you appropriately!
In Search of the Sacred Gospel
Thanks...! You know, I'm actually planning on proposing to my indecisive boyfriend! These will take him down memory lane and just like that I'll have him!
Hey! You over there! Wait up! I urgently need Snow Shards and Holy Bells! Can you give me some? Please!
Gather âround the Xmas Tree
The decorations are up! That means it's time for a party with everyone! Merry Xmas...!
Sorry, would anyone like to help me decorate a Xmas tree?
Act 1: Bad News From a Snowy Mountain
You've been already?! Thank you!âª Wait, what...? No way... Anyway, take this token of appreciation!
There's a snowman running loose up on Mt Snowpeak! I hope you'll go investigate!
Act 2: Growing Unease
What's the situation then...? The snowman up there... Could it be "That Kid"...?
I'm still a bit worried... Could you please go back up there and investigate some more? My tone changed? I'm just plain-old Snow now!
Act 3: An Unexpected Reunion
Wait... so it is really my friend Yukki...! But it doesn't recognize me anymore...
That out-of-control snowman... must be my friend...! I'm going up there with you this time!
Act 4: Prayer
Yukki had a slight reaction to my voice! Is there any way to make it have a breakthrough and realize who I am...?!
Let's get closer to Yukki! It must be under some kind of evil enchantment!
Act 5: An important Friend
Yukki's magic is weakening! I can feel it very faintly... Almost there... just hang on a little longer!
I've never had any friends. Yukki was my first. So... I'm not giving up!
Act 6: Snatches of a Remembered Song
Yukki's back! That old song was the breakthrough! Thank you so much!âª
There's a song Yukki and I once sang together. That will work! I'll sing that song...!
A Fishing Rod of Happiness
You've done a good job enhancinging it. I can see that... This is a gift to thank you.
It's not very easy to use, but I think you'll be able to properly enhance this fishing rod.
New Year Necessities â
All right, time to begin! Watch me do it... that's it! Here you go, thanks for helping out!
You can't have a New Year without rice cakes! I want to make beautiful rice cakes~! Can you help me out?
New Year Necessities â¡
Okay, let's get started! Ta-da...! All done! I'm so happy~! Here's your gift!
Shoji are a must for Far-East-style rooms! Now, let's take on a Shoji-crafting challenge!
Lucky Money?
I'll just give you this stone I found on the beach. Stones were once used as money you know. Ahahaha!
